title: Aaron Hernandez lawyers ask for search warrant to be tossed
text: > Top News Aaron Hernandez lawyers ask for search warrant to be tossed James Sultan, defense attorney for former New England Patriots NFL football player Aaron Hernandez, addresses the court during a hearing at Suffolk Superior Court in Boston, Wednesday, Oct. 6, 2015. Lawyers for Hernandez have asked a judge to throw out a search warrant that led police to seize a vehicle that prosecutors say Hernandez was driving when he fatally shot two Boston men in 2012. (Matt Stone/The Boston Herald via AP, Pool)
